entries.journal_entry_description: Speak with Boss Nass about an Old Republic battle droid that used an experimental Old Republic droid module, a Stochastic Decision Chip.
entries.journal_entry_title: Old Republic Droid Modules: The Gungan Battle Droid
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Droid Module 4: The Stochastic Decision Chip is in a battle droid that fell into the hands of the Ultragungan Militia. Speak to Boss Nass to find out what you'll need to do to get that droid module.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Droid Module 4: Seek Boss Nass' Assistance
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Droid Module 4: According to Boss Nass, you'll need to find a way to disable the battle droid's self-destruct response when you attempt to remove the Stochastic Decision Chip.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Droid Module 4: Acquire the Stochastic Decision Chip from the droid in the Ultragungan Militia bunker.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Droid Module 4: Acquire the Stochastic Decision Chip
entries.task05_comm_message_text: [BEGIN TRANSMISSION]: Please return to the RSF mainframe in Theed. [END TRANSMISSION]
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Return to Theed and update the RSF mainframe information about acquisition of the Stochastic Decision Chip.
entries.task06_journal_entry_title: Return to the RSF Mainframe in Theed
